episodes.title: Surviving a Cult: Journey to Freedom
episodes.description:
Today we welcome Maitre, a survivor of abuse, cult upbringing and more. Hear us discuss her life dealing with mental health in a society that refused it. Her candid discussion provides deep insights into the struggles and triumphs of those going through so much. 

💬 Engage With Us:
What's your experience with being open about mental health? Share your thoughts and join the discussion below. Your input is invaluable as we continue to break down barriers together.

🔔 Stay Updated:
Subscribe to our channel and hit the notification bell to keep up with our ongoing discussions on mental health. Follow us for more episodes that challenge perceptions and provide deep insights into the mental health landscape.

#podcast #mentalhealth #healing
